1. On *ćuti* tokom časa. (He is silent during the lesson.)
2. Ona *ćuti* već deset minuta. (She has been silent for ten minutes.)
3. Oni su se dogovorili da *ćute*. (They agreed to keep quiet.)
4. Njegov otac ga je naterao da *ćuti*. (His father forced him to be quiet.)
5. Ona nije mogla da *ćuti*. (She couldn't keep quiet.)
6. Njegova sestra je stalno *ćutala*. (His sister was always quiet.)
7. On je naredio deci da *ćute*. (He ordered the children to be quiet.)
8. Ona je mogla da *ćuti* čitavu noć. (She could stay quiet all night.)